title: 616. The Genius of the Rams Offense & Why the Bucs are in Trouble
itunes:title: 616. The Genius of the Rams Offense & Why the Bucs are in Trouble
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys react to the MNF game between the Rams and Buccaneers, while while focusing on the Rams wide receivers and looking at where the team spent their money (6:11). After that, the duo focus on the Buccaneers and explain why the team could be in trouble (24:11). To wrap up the show, the pair give their analysis on how Ohio State QB Justin Fields played against Indiana and also evaluate Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence (32:44).
